NK036(chi)011:0: spros med dbang gi ti ka bzhugs so lung med
NK036(chi)011:1: bcom ldan 'das spros pa thams cad nye bar zhi
NK036(chi)011:2: ba'i dpal rdo rje 'chang la phyag 'tshal lo dad
NK036(chi)011:3: pa rab dang ldan pa'i skal ldan nges pa'i lus
NK036(chi)011:4: can nyid rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i don la
NK036(chi)011:5: yang rmongs pa med cing 'jug sgo bsal bya'i phyir
NK036(chi)011:6: phra tig mig gi rin chen rgyan spras pa'i dbang
NK036(chi)011:7: bzhi rdzogs par byed pa'i don nyid du spros la
NK036(chi)011:8: dga' ba'i don du de bstan nas da ni spros
NK036(chi)011:9: pa dag dang bral ba'i don du yang spros med
NK036(chi)011:10: dbang gi man ngag gnad nyid ni 'di ltar dam
NK036(chi)011:11: tshig ldan pas nges par gzung bar bya gal te
NK036(chi)011:12: skal ba dang ldan pa'i skyes bus dbang bzhi rdzogs
NK036(chi)011:13: par byed pa'am yang na spros pa la mi dga'
NK036(chi)011:14: ba rnams la 'di ltar spros pa med pa'i dbang
NK036(chi)011:15: bskur bas rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i dbang bskur
NK036(chi)011:16: 'di snod dang ldan pa'i skal lda na gnyis sam
NK036(chi)011:17: gsum las mang na dam tshig gi chad pa 'bab
NK036(chi)011:18: bo 'di lta bu'i dad pa can 'khor ba las
NK036(chi)011:19: blo ldog pa rang bzhin gyis sos dal zhing rang
NK036(chi)011:20: shugs bzang ba rnam par rtog pa bgas kyis chung
NK036(chi)011:21: ba 'dod pa chung zhing chog shes pa can rang
NK036(chi)011:22: bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i snod yin pas 'di lta
NK036(chi)011:23: bu'i slob ma gcig gam gnyis nas gsum man chad
NK036(chi)011:24: la bskur ba'o de la sngon du bya ba'i sdom
NK036(chi)011:25: pa dang dngos gzhi'i bya ba'i rim pa'o de nas
NK036(chi)011:26: bla ma nyid la slob mas dbang gi zhu ba
NK036(chi)011:27: phul nas de nyid la gus pa 'jog pa'i phyir
NK036(chi)011:28: du rang gi bla ma la dbang bskyar la zhu
NK036(chi)011:29: ba dang gal te mi bzhugs na bla ma nyid
NK036(chi)011:30: nam mkhar dmigs te spros pa med pa'i dbang rnams
NK036(chi)011:31: yid kyis blang ngo brgyud pa'i bla ma rnams la
NK036(chi)011:32: gsol ba gdab par bya ba dang ngag gi dri
NK036(chi)011:33: ma dag par bya ba'i phyir yi ge gsam la
NK036(chi)011:34: ngag 'byongs par bya ba dang gnyis su med pa'i
NK036(chi)011:35: don la blo bskyed par bya ba'i phyir ye shes
NK036(chi)011:36: lnga'i mtshan nyidabasgoma pa dang 'khor ba la yid dbyung
NK036(chi)011:37: bar bya ba'i phyir mi rtag pa bsgom pa dang
NK036(chi)011:38: spyod lam gyis rjes su bzung ba'i phyir bya byed
NK036(chi)011:39: kyi spyod pa nyer gcig brtsam par bya ba dang
NK036(chi)011:40: lta ba'i don dran par bya ba'i phyir stong pa
NK036(chi)011:41: nyid bsgom pa la sogs pa ni slob dpon gyi
NK036(chi)011:42: sngon du 'gro ba'i las so de ltar rdo rje
NK036(chi)011:43: slob dpon gyis sngon du 'gro ba'i las rnams byas
NK036(chi)011:44: nas slob ma dad pa dang ldan pa de yang
NK036(chi)011:45: 'khor ba las yid dbyung bar bya ba'i phyir mi
NK036(chi)011:46: rtog pa bsgom pa'i las rnams bslabs te bsgom du
NK036(chi)011:47: gzhug go de yang zhag lnga'am dagu'am bcu gcig gi
NK036(chi)011:48: bar du bsgom du gzhug go de ltar bsgoms pas
NK036(chi)011:49: dad pa drag po skye ba dang 'khor ba las
NK036(chi)011:50: yid dbyung sgyid lug pa dang nges par 'byung bar
NK036(chi)011:51: nges so de nas slob dpon gyis 'khor ba'i nyes
NK036(chi)011:52: dmigs rnams dang sangs rgyas kyi yon tan rnams bshad
NK036(chi)011:53: la spros pa med pa'i dbang bskur ba'i gnas rab
NK036(chi)011:54: tu dben par dpon slob rnams phyin te gnas khang
NK036(chi)011:55: gi nang thams cad dri sna tshogs kyis chag chag
NK036(chi)011:56: gdab pa dang man+dala zlum po me long gi ngos
NK036(chi)011:57: ltar mnyam pa ra byas la de nyid kyi dbus
NK036(chi)011:58: su rdul tshon gyis bum pa dmar po kha rgyan
NK036(chi)011:59: dang mgul chings dang bcas pa dag bris la zlum
NK036(chi)011:60: zhing mnyam pa tshon sna lnga'i ra bas bskor de'i
NK036(chi)011:61: shar phyogs su shing khri'i steng du rin po che'i
NK036(chi)011:62: bum pa gas pa dang chag pa dang zhom pa
NK036(chi)011:63: med par gsum gyi nang du sman sna tshogs pa
NK036(chi)011:64: dang dri sna tshogs pa dang mar dang 'o ma
NK036(chi)011:65: la sogs pas bkang la 'bras bu dang me tog
NK036(chi)011:66: can gyi shing gi kha rgyan byas la ras dkar
NK036(chi)011:67: po dri ma med pa gsum gyis mgul ba bcing
NK036(chi)011:68: ngo de ltar bum pa re re'i steng du rma
NK036(chi)011:69: bya'i mdongs gsum gsum dang me long dang man shel
NK036(chi)011:70: gsum gsum bzhag par bya'o mar me dang lha bshos
NK036(chi)011:71: la sogs pa bdun las mi nyung bar byas la
NK036(chi)011:72: de nas slob ma rnams phyi rol nas las bum
NK036(chi)011:73: gyii khrus chu nas bton la gos gsar pa gyon
NK036(chi)011:74: pa la sogs pa rgyan dag gis legs par brgyan
NK036(chi)011:75: cing gral la legs par 'khod de bgegs kyi bar
NK036(chi)011:76: chad zhi bar bya ba'i phyir las kyi slob dpon
NK036(chi)011:77: gyis gu gul gyi dud pas bdug de nas spros
NK036(chi)011:78: pa med pa'i dbang bskur ba'i don du gser gyi
NK036(chi)011:79: man+dala dbul zhing thal mo sbyar nas bla ma rdo
NK036(chi)011:80: rje 'dzin pa ni khams gsum 'khor ba'i gnyen gcig
NK036(chi)011:81: pu 'gro ba mgon med rnams kyi skyabs thar pa'i
NK036(chi)011:82: lam skas chen po ste ma riig sel pa'i sgron
NK036(chi)011:83: me la mun pa'i tshogs bdag skyabs su mchi 'khor
NK036(chi)011:84: ba 'dam gyi tshogs nang du bying pa skyabs med
NK036(chi)011:85: bdag la skyobs dug gsum nyi mas rlan bral bas
NK036(chi)011:86: thugs rje'i chu rgyun bdag la phob rtsub 'gyur me
NK036(chi)011:87: chen 'bar ba la rang byung rlan gyis bsil bar
NK036(chi)011:88: mdzod ces brjod du gzhug ste las kyi slob dpon
NK036(chi)011:89: gyis rdo rjes drangs te gral la 'khod du gzhug
NK036(chi)011:90: gus pas 'dug par bya'o phyag len ni nyams su
NK036(chi)011:91: len pa'i gang zag slob dpon dang slob ma'i mtshan
NK036(chi)011:92: nyid skyon yon rnams bstan nas nyams su blang bya'i
NK036(chi)011:93: gdams pa la bla ma brgyud pa'i lo rgyus bshad
NK036(chi)011:94: de slob mas phyag dang bshags pa byas nas mkha'
NK036(chi)011:95: 'gro ma dmar mo bsgoms la rig 'dzin dang rigs
NK036(chi)011:96: lnga'i byin 'bebs byas nas man+dala phul nas gsol ba
NK036(chi)011:97: btab ste slob dpon gyis chos bshad pa ni /
NK036(chi)011:98: de nas 'khor ba'i mtshan nyid rnams bstan par bya
NK036(chi)011:99: ste de'ang slob dpon gyi gling las khyad par 'phags
NK036(chi)011:100: te 'dzam bu'i gling du skyes thob par dka' ba'i
NK036(chi)011:101: mi lus rin po che thob 'dug par dka' ba'i
NK036(chi)011:102: sh+aakya thub pa'i bstan pa la gnas 'phrad par dka'
NK036(chi)011:103: ba'i dam pa'i chos rin po che dang 'phrad nas
NK036(chi)011:104: chos ma byas na mi tshe stong log yin pas
NK036(chi)011:105: da res tshe 'di la rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas rin
NK036(chi)011:106: po che thob par byas la sems can thams cad
NK036(chi)011:107: thugs rje'i sgo nas 'dren dgos pas da res tshe
NK036(chi)011:108: 'di la thob par bya'o snyam pa'i blo bskyed nas
NK036(chi)011:109: smin pa'i las la 'jug dgos de grol bar byed
NK036(chi)011:110: pa'i thabs kho na la gnas par byas nas mthar
NK036(chi)011:111: sangs rgyas sgrub par 'dod pas na dang po gzhi
NK036(chi)011:112: ma smin pa smin par byed pa la dbang bzhi
NK036(chi)011:113: rdzogs par thob dgos pas 'di zhu'o des ma grub
NK036(chi)011:114: na spros med man chad thob par byas nas nyams
NK036(chi)011:115: su blang dgos de nas 'khor ba'i mtshan nyid yid
NK036(chi)011:116: la dran par byas nas 'das pa la zhugs te
NK036(chi)011:117: de yang 'khor ba'i mtshan nyid de las ldog par
NK036(chi)011:118: bya ba'i phyir du 'khor ba'i zhen pa dang bral
NK036(chi)011:119: bar bya ste chos thams cad rmi lam lta bu
NK036(chi)011:120: sgyu ma lta bu sprul pa lta bu dri za'i
NK036(chi)011:121: grong khyer lta bu bar snang gi glog lta bu
NK036(chi)011:122: myur byed kyi 'khor lo lta bu dpe du mas
NK036(chi)011:123: mtshon par bya'o de nyid kyi don gyis 'khor ba'i
NK036(chi)011:124: zhen pa dang bral ba'i gong ma'i don la gnas
NK036(chi)011:125: pa'i dgos pa yod do yang 'khor ba las skyo
NK036(chi)011:126: ba skyed pa las 'khor ba'i mtshan nyid ni 'dod
NK036(chi)011:127: pa dang bral bar bya ba'i phyir 'khor ba la
NK036(chi)011:128: zhen pa'i skyon de yang spang bar bya'o 'khor ba'i
NK036(chi)011:129: dpe zo chu'i khyud mo'i rnam pa dang mtshungs me
NK036(chi)011:130: chen 'bar ba'i nang du sbrang bu tshud pa lta
NK036(chi)011:131: bu'o 'dab chags rnyi la tshud pa lta bu dang
NK036(chi)011:132: ri dwags rgya la tshud pa lta bu dang phyi'i
NK036(chi)011:133: rgya mtsho la gzings thag chad la lta bu dang
NK036(chi)011:134: rab tu brgal dka' ba'i 'dam rdzab chen por tshud
NK036(chi)011:135: pa lta bu dang 'jigs pa dang bcas pa'i 'phrang
NK036(chi)011:136: la lam nor ba lta bu dang gsod pa'i gshed
NK036(chi)011:137: ma'i dkyil du tshud pa lta bu dang de la
NK036(chi)011:138: sogs pa bstan no yang 'dod yon la skyo ba
NK036(chi)011:139: skyed pa'i phyir 'dod yon ni skom gyis gdungs pa
NK036(chi)011:140: la tsha chu blud pa lta bu dug gi lo
NK036(chi)011:141: ma lta bu sbrul gyis zin pa lta bu spu
NK036(chi)011:142: gri'i so lta bu bud med kyi 'dod chags lta
NK036(chi)011:143: bu la sogs pas 'khor lo'i mtshan nyid bstan no
NK036(chi)011:144: 'di rnams las dang po ba dbang la 'jug pa'i
NK036(chi)011:145: sngon du bstan par bya 'khor ba'i mtshan nyid sangs
NK036(chi)011:146: rgyas kyi yon tan la sogs pa sngon du bshad
NK036(chi)011:147: do spros pa med pa'i dbang bskur ba la sngon
NK036(chi)011:148: du 'jug pa'i cho ga dang dngos gzhi gnyis yin
NK036(chi)011:149: te thun mong gi 'jug pa dang thun mong ma
NK036(chi)011:150: yin pa'i 'jug pa'o thun mong gi 'jug pa la
NK036(chi)011:151: sngon du bla ma la gsol ba gdab pa ni
NK036(chi)011:152: bla ma rdo rje 'dzin pa rnams dgongs su gsol
NK036(chi)011:153: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' rnams
NK036(chi)011:154: te rjo rje dang rin po che dang pad+ma dang
NK036(chi)011:155: las dang bde bar gshegs pa'i rigs thams cad bdag
NK036(chi)011:156: la dgong su gsol bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi ba
NK036(chi)011:157: / dus 'di nas bzung ste snying po byang chub
NK036(chi)011:158: la mchis kyi bar du bla ma rdo rje 'dzin
NK036(chi)011:159: pa chen pos bdag gi lus byin gyis brlab tu
NK036(chi)011:160: gsol gang bar mdzad du gsol rgyas par byin gyis
NK036(chi)011:161: brlab tu gsol smin par byin gyis brlab tu gsol
NK036(chi)011:162: gang bar byin gyis brlab tu gsol rgyas par byin
NK036(chi)011:163: gyis brlab tu gsol cher 'phel bar mdzad du gsol
NK036(chi)011:164: zhes gsol ba gdab bo yang bla ma la gsol
NK036(chi)011:165: ba btab la dam bca' ba'i tshig 'di rnams khas
NK036(chi)011:166: blang bar bya'o bla ma rdo rje 'dzin pa chen
NK036(chi)011:167: po rnams dgongs su gsol phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas dang
NK036(chi)011:168: byang chub sems dpa' rnams te rdo rje dang rin
NK036(chi)011:169: po che dang pad+ma dang las dang de bzhin gshegs
NK036(chi)011:170: pa'i rigs rnams dgongs su gsol dus 'di nas bzung
NK036(chi)011:171: nas snying po byang chub la mchis kyi bar du
NK036(chi)011:172: sangs rgyas chos dang dge 'dun te bla na med
NK036(chi)011:173: pa'i dkon mchog gsum bla ma la yang phyag 'tshal
NK036(chi)011:174: lo bla ma rdo rje 'dzin pa dang dkon mchog
NK036(chi)011:175: gsum la skyabs su mchi sdig pa thams cad so
NK036(chi)011:176: sor bshags byang chub sems ni bla na med dam
NK036(chi)011:177: pa bdag gis bskyed par bgyi rigs lnga'i dam tshig
NK036(chi)011:178: rjes bzung ste rdo rje dril bu la sogs pa
NK036(chi)011:179: dam tshig rdzas rnams gzung bar bgyi sangs rgyas chos
NK036(chi)011:180: dang dge 'dun te bla na med pa'i dkon mchog
NK036(chi)011:181: gsum nam du yang ni mi btang ngo rdo rje
NK036(chi)011:182: slob dpon mi gtong ngo rdo rje spun sring rnams
NK036(chi)011:183: la yang nam yang smad par mi bya'o sems can
NK036(chi)011:184: rnams la 'tshe ba spang 'phags pa rnams la smad
NK036(chi)011:185: mi bgyi nyan thos rang sangs rgyas rnams la cung
NK036(chi)011:186: zad brnyas par mi bya zhing sngags 'chang spang bar
NK036(chi)011:187: mi bya'o bsnyen sgrub las kyi mtha' rnams kyang 'di
NK036(chi)011:188: dus nyid nas gzung bar bya dam tshig sdom pa
NK036(chi)011:189: la gnas shing sku gsung thugs las mi 'ada'o srog
NK036(chi)011:190: chags gsad par mi bya zhing dam chos nam yang
NK036(chi)011:191: mi btang ngo bla ma'i bya ba mi btang zhing
NK036(chi)011:192: 'khrul pa'i bya ba mi bagyi'o sems can smin pa
NK036(chi)011:193: nyid du bgyi ma grol ba rnams dgrol ba dang
NK036(chi)011:194: ma bsgral ba rnams bsgral bar bgyi dbugs ma phyung
NK036(chi)011:195: rnams dbugs dbyungs ste sems can mya ngan 'das la
NK036(chi)011:196: 'god bstan pa smad par mi bya zhing bla ma
NK036(chi)011:197: la yang yon dbul lo 'khor ba ring du spang
NK036(chi)011:198: bya zhing myang 'das dang du blang bar bgyi dge
NK036(chi)011:199: slob sems sun mi dbyung zhing bsam gtan bsgom pa
NK036(chi)011:200: dkrug mi bya chos dang gang zag la mi smad
NK036(chi)011:201: khyad par da la bsgom par bgyi rdzogs rim bsgom
NK036(chi)011:202: las mi 'ada'o ji ltar bla mas gsungs pa la
NK036(chi)011:203: bdag ni nam yang mi 'ada'o zhes pa bla ma'i
NK036(chi)011:204: mdun dag tu dam baca'i tshig dang gsol gdab brjod
NK036(chi)011:205: de nas slob dpon bdag nyid kyis thod pa tshal
NK036(chi)011:206: bu'i nang dag tu bdud rtsi lnga yi chu blugs
NK036(chi)011:207: la lag tu bzung ste 'di skad brjod h'u 'di
NK036(chi)011:208: ni dam tshig dmyal ba'i chu dam tshig 'das na
NK036(chi)011:209: 'tshig par 'gyur thur bltas dmyal khams me yis bsreg
NK036(chi)011:210: bskal pa bgrang gis mi langs par sdug bsngal chen
NK036(chi)011:211: po myong bar 'gyur de bas dam tshig srog gi
NK036(chi)011:212: chu snying la bzhag pas thub par gyis gal te
NK036(chi)011:213: nyams par ma gyur na 'di ni dam tshig dngos
NK036(chi)011:214: grub chu mchog dang thun mong longs spyod cing rdzogs
NK036(chi)011:215: pa'i sangs rgyas 'bras bu thob des na 'di nyid
NK036(chi)011:216: thub par gyis zhes brjod dam tshig mna' bgag mna'
NK036(chi)011:217: chu blug go rdo rje chen po'i gsang tshig ni
NK036(chi)011:218: slob mas 'di skad brjod par bya bdag ni 'di
NK036(chi)011:219: nas bzung nas su byang chub ma thob bar dag
NK036(chi)011:220: tu 'khrul pa'i bya ba byed re kan bla mas
NK036(chi)011:221: ci gsung mi nyan re sems can kun la 'tshe
NK036(chi)011:222: re kan bde chen lam du mi slong re 'jig
NK036(chi)011:223: rten 'dod phyir 'breng re kan lta ba sgom dang
NK036(chi)011:224: spyod pa ni srog gi phyir yang gtang re kan
NK036(chi)011:225: dur khrod la sogs dben pa'i gnas 'di nas bzung
NK036(chi)011:226: nas mi bsten re mdor na 'jig rten bya ba
NK036(chi)011:227: btang 'das pa'i bya ba gtong re kan zhes ni
NK036(chi)011:228: slob mas rim pa bzhin rdo rje'i dam tshig mna'
NK036(chi)011:229: bskyal lo bla ma dpal ldan rdo rje 'chang mna'
NK036(chi)011:230: yi nyes dmigs bshad du gsol thub pa'i yon tan
NK036(chi)011:231: legs bshad de de nas bla mas sdom pa dpog
NK036(chi)011:232: cing dam bca' ba'i tshig rnams brjod par bya'o kye
NK036(chi)011:233: skal ldan sems kyi bu cig nyon phyii nang gsang
NK036(chi)011:234: ba'i theg pa dang dam chos bsgrub pa dam chos
NK036(chi)011:235: shig sems can kun la byams pa'i sems dus 'di
NK036(chi)011:236: nyid nas ma spang zhig dkyil 'khor 'khor lo bsgom
NK036(chi)011:237: pa dang bla ma nam yang ma btang zhig rdo
NK036(chi)011:238: rje mched la mi khro zhing sangs rgyas chos dang
NK036(chi)011:239: dge 'dun te dkon mchog gsum po bkur ba dang
NK036(chi)011:240: ji ltar sngags kyi dam tshig dang sdom pa thams
NK036(chi)011:241: cad bzung bar gyis bstan pa kun la gnod pa
NK036(chi)011:242: spongs thar pa'i lam du 'gro bar gyis kyee skal
NK036(chi)011:243: ldan rdzogs pa'i rang bzhin can dbang bskur cho ga
NK036(chi)011:244: ji lta bar gzhan la brjod par ma byed cig
NK036(chi)011:245: dam rdzas rnams dang sngags kyi tshig dbang bskur ma
NK036(chi)011:246: thob mi rnams la nam yang bshad par ma byed
NK036(chi)011:247: ka 'khor ba ring du spang bar gyis gang gi
NK036(chi)011:248: rdo rjo 'dzin pa yis dngos grub rnams ni ma
NK036(chi)011:249: btang zhig ces brjod la sdom pa dpog par bya'o
NK036(chi)011:250: mi dge ba la sogs pa spong ba'i chos ni
NK036(chi)011:251: bya ba'i rim pa bshad de yan chad thun mong
NK036(chi)011:252: gi 'jug pa rdzogs nas da thun mong ma yin
NK036(chi)011:254: spros pa la dga' na rigs lnga'i sdom pa dpog
NK036(chi)011:255: de nas bla ma la gsol ba gdab par bya
NK036(chi)011:256: ste ras sam dar gyis gdong g.yogs shing bla ma
NK036(chi)011:257: rdo rje 'dzin pa la bdag ni skal ldan snying
NK036(chi)011:258: gi bu dad pas rab tu nyan par 'tshal rang
NK036(chi)011:259: bzhin rdzogs pa chen po yi dbang bskur nang du
NK036(chi)011:260: 'jug pa ni dpa' bo rdo rje bla ma yis
NK036(chi)011:261: rang gi sems kyi gnas lugs kyi a ti'i da
NK036(chi)011:262: la bstan du gsol bdag ni yang dag 'dir bzhug
NK036(chi)011:263: nas slar yang ldog par mi bgyid do zhes gsol
NK036(chi)011:264: ba gdab de nas bla mas rjes su gnang ba
NK036(chi)011:265: sbyin te e ma bu khyod skal ba bzang skal
NK036(chi)011:266: ldan byang chub sems chen po sngon chad rang bzhin
NK036(chi)011:267: rdzogs chen gyi dbang bskur nang du ma zhugs pas
NK036(chi)011:268: do nub skal ldan bu khyod la rdzogs chen dkyil
NK036(chi)011:269: 'khor bstan par bya sems kyi rtog pa kun sol
NK036(chi)011:270: la 'jig rten bcings pa kun grol gyis 'di la
NK036(chi)011:271: spang blang snyad dang bral rigs dang rgyud rnams sbyong
NK036(chi)011:272: ba yi lus ngag bde ba'i rten yin pas deng
NK036(chi)011:273: nas brtsams te slar ma ldog ces rjes su gnang
NK036(chi)011:274: ba sbyin nas man+dala gyi shar phyogs su lus gnad
NK036(chi)011:275: tsog pu thal mo sbyar nas sems ma yengs par
NK036(chi)011:276: bla ma la gtad nas bsgom du gzhug de ni
NK036(chi)011:277: bsre ba thun mong ma yin pa ste rdzogs pa
NK036(chi)011:278: chen po mnyam pa'i rgyas gdab pa ces so bkod
NK036(chi)011:279: pa yid bzhin nor bu rin po che 'byung ba'i
NK036(chi)011:280: rgyud las bla ma rdo rje 'dzin pa ni khams
NK036(chi)011:281: gsum 'khor ba'i gnyen gcig pu 'gro ba mgon med
NK036(chi)011:282: rnams kyi skyabs thar pa'i lam skas chen po ste
NK036(chi)011:283: ma rig sel ba'i sgron me la mun pa'i tshogs
NK036(chi)011:284: bdag skyabs su mchi 'khor ba 'dam gyi tshogs nang
NK036(chi)011:285: du bying ba skyabs med bdag la skyobs dus gsum
NK036(chi)011:286: me yi rlan bral ba'i sdug bsngal skam la gnas
NK036(chi)011:287: pa la thugs rje'i chu rgyun bdag la phob rtsub
NK036(chi)011:288: 'gyur dmyal ba'i me chen 'bar rang byung rgyun gyis
NK036(chi)011:289: bsil bar mdzod de nas gdong yogs bkrol byin dbab
NK036(chi)011:290: man+dala de'i tho phyi rnams lha bshos dang mar me
NK036(chi)011:291: dang spos la sogs pa ci 'byor ba'i yo byad
NK036(chi)011:292: dang mkha' 'gro ma rnams mnyes par bya ba dang
NK036(chi)011:293: bar chad bsal ba'i bya ba'i phyir tshogs dang gtor
NK036(chi)011:294: ma rab tu bzang ba bsham par bya'o de nas
NK036(chi)011:295: spros pa med pa'i dbang bskur ba ni ngag gi
NK036(chi)011:296: nus pa gzhug pa dang ngag rang dag la 'gro
NK036(chi)011:297: ba'i don yin te dpon slob kun so so'i lus
NK036(chi)011:298: bde bar bcos la ngag tu sgra che ba yang
NK036(chi)011:299: ma yin chung ba yang ma yin par a a
NK036(chi)011:300: zhes brjod cing yid a la gtad pas zhag gcig
NK036(chi)011:301: brjod par bya de nas nub gnyis pa la +aa
NK036(chi)011:302: li'i tshogs tshang bar brjod de nas nub gsum pa
NK036(chi)011:303: la k+aa li'i tshogs tshang bar brjod par bya'o 'di'i
NK036(chi)011:304: dus na slob dpon gyis a rkyang pa'i dus na
NK036(chi)011:305: bu yis a brjod bas rtsa rnams kha phye ste
NK036(chi)011:306: a thol thol rang 'byung de las 'od kyi gong
NK036(chi)011:307: bu rnams las 'od 'phros pas rang bzhin gyi kun
NK036(chi)011:308: tu bzang po'i sbyor ba'i brdas bskul kun bzang yab
NK036(chi)011:309: yum sbyor mtshams nas byang chub kyi sems 'od lnga'i
NK036(chi)011:310: gong bus rang gi mgo mjug khyab pa la blo
NK036(chi)011:311: bzhag 'di'i dus na rna ba'i sgra 'byung ba'i 'od
NK036(chi)011:312: btsir ro de ltar slob ma rang yang bsgom du
NK036(chi)011:313: gzhug go bcugs pas nyams su myong ba khyad par
NK036(chi)011:314: can skye bar nges so de nas +aa li'i tshogs
NK036(chi)011:315: brjod pa'i dus na 'di nyid brjod pa tsam gyis
NK036(chi)011:316: rtsa rnams kyi nang nas rang bzhin gyi yi ge
NK036(chi)011:317: rnams rang byung rang gi ngag nas kyang chos thams
NK036(chi)011:318: cad kyi sgra si li li byung ba la blo
NK036(chi)011:319: bzhag k+aa li'i dus su brjod pa'i yi ge de
NK036(chi)011:320: dag phyir mngon par rang gi khog pa'i nang yi
NK036(chi)011:321: ges mer gyis khengs pa la blo bzhag par bya'o
NK036(chi)011:322: de nas skal ldan la dbang bskur bar bya ste
NK036(chi)011:323: lus ngag yid gsum ka byin gyis brlab pa'i don
NK036(chi)011:324: du dbang bskur ba ni lus gcer bur phyung la
NK036(chi)011:325: bum pa'i chu dang sin+d+hu ra'i thig le zhig spyi
NK036(chi)011:326: bo'i gtsug tu byas la ngag tu +amo +amo zhes
NK036(chi)011:327: drag tu brjod du gzhug slob dpon gyis mgrin pa'i
NK036(chi)011:328: rtsa gtems 'di'i dus su lus 'dar zhing g.yo ba
NK036(chi)011:329: dang ngag rang rdol ba dang sems bag yang su
NK036(chi)011:330: 'gyur ba nyid 'byung slob dpon gyis slob ma'i lus
NK036(chi)011:331: +amo dkar po chen po zhig tu dmigs la de
NK036(chi)011:332: 'od du zhu ba la chos nyid stong pa'i rgyas
NK036(chi)011:333: gdab slob dpon gyis bum pa'i chu thigs pa dang
NK036(chi)011:334: sin+d+hu ra'i thig le zhig mgrin par byas la slob
NK036(chi)011:335: ma'i ngag tu drag shul dang bcas pas +aah+aahbarjoda do
NK036(chi)011:336: slob dpon gyis slob ma'i mchan khung gi rtsa gtems
NK036(chi)011:337: slob ma'i shes pa nam mkhar gtod du gzhug 'di'i
NK036(chi)011:338: dus su lus rab tu 'dar ba dang ngag rab
NK036(chi)011:339: tu 'dar ba dang sems rab tu gsal ba dag
NK036(chi)011:340: 'ong slob ma'i lus la +aa dmar po chen po
NK036(chi)011:341: gcig tu dmigs la chos nyid stong pa nyid kyis
NK036(chi)011:342: rgyas gdab yang slob dpon gyis bum pa'i chu thigs
NK036(chi)011:343: gcig dang sin+d+hu ra'i thig le snying khar byas la
NK036(chi)011:344: ngag tu h'u zhes drag tu brjod du gzhug bla
NK036(chi)011:345: mas bu'i nu ma'i rtsa gtems shes pa 'byung ba
NK036(chi)011:346: bzhi la gtad slob ma'i lus h'u zhig tu dmigs
NK036(chi)011:347: la chos nyid kyis rgyas gdab po de yang rtsa
NK036(chi)011:348: gtems pa gsum la mgrin pa'i rtsa lag len du
NK036(chi)011:349: gtems gzhan gnyis mi 'dug pas mi gtems gzhan rnams
NK036(chi)011:350: ji lta ba bzhin du bya'o de nas tsan dan
NK036(chi)011:351: dkar po'i thig le smin mtshams su byug de'i steng
NK036(chi)011:352: du dmar po thig le bya de'i rjes la stong
NK036(chi)011:353: nyid dar cig bsgom de nas bum pa'i yi ge'i
NK036(chi)011:354: rang bzhin du dmigs pa la slob ma'i mgrin pa'i
NK036(chi)011:355: gnas su ngag la bstim chu dang sman la sogs
NK036(chi)011:356: pa rnams las rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i mtshan
NK036(chi)011:357: nyid kyi rang sgra byung ste chos thams cad brjod
NK036(chi)011:358: du med pa'o bsam du med pa'o bltar med pa'o
NK036(chi)011:359: mtshan ma med pa'o smon pa med pa'o spros pa
NK036(chi)011:360: med pa'o spros pa'i mtha' brgyad dang bral ba'o zhes
NK036(chi)011:361: pa'i sgrar 'byung bas slob mas kyang de nyid kyis
NK036(chi)011:362: rang bzhin du gyur par dmigs la de nas slob
NK036(chi)011:363: dpon gyis bum pa slob ma'i spyi bor bzhag la
NK036(chi)011:364: dmigs pa dang tshig rnams ngag tu brjod cing bya'o
NK036(chi)011:365: de nas ngag gi las sgrib rdzogs par bya ba'i
NK036(chi)011:366: phyir nyi zla kha sbyor ram gzhan gyis shes kyang
NK036(chi)011:367: gtub rdo rje'i glu lan gsum brjod gzhan yang dung
NK036(chi)011:368: dang cha lang dang 'khar rnga dang shing rnga dang
NK036(chi)011:369: dril bu dang d+aa ma ru la sogs pa dus
NK036(chi)011:370: gcig la bsgrag cing yi ge brgya pa bazla'o de
NK036(chi)011:371: nas tshig brgyad kyi don bshad do de nas slob
NK036(chi)011:372: ma'i ngag la tshigs su bcad pa'i dbang bskur bar
NK036(chi)011:373: bya ste rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen pos mnyam pa'i
NK036(chi)011:374: rgyas gdab pa'i phyir tshig gi rgyal po 'di dag
NK036(chi)011:375: ngar bskyed la brjod par bya'o e ma hoh chos
NK036(chi)011:376: nyid spros dang bral ba'i bde chen de bltas med
NK036(chi)011:377: bsam yul 'das pa ngo mtshar che gnyis med rang
NK036(chi)011:378: snang kun khyab ye shes ni rang rig mngon du
NK036(chi)011:379: 'ong ba ngo mtshar che bya bral rang bzhin rdzogs
NK036(chi)011:380: chen gnas lugs nyid ma btsal rang las byung ba
NK036(chi)011:381: ngo mtshar che ngo bo spros bral rang bzhin rnam
NK036(chi)011:382: dag la dge sdig mtha' las 'das pa ngo mtshar
NK036(chi)011:383: che rang snang spros pa med pa'i rig pa nyid
NK036(chi)011:384: lta sgom spyod par snang ba ngo mtshar che rang
NK036(chi)011:385: las byung ba 'od kyi sgron me 'di mngon sum
NK036(chi)011:386: yul du snang ba ngo mtshar che ngo bo rang
NK036(chi)011:387: bzhin thugs rje phyogs med pas chos sku longs sku
NK036(chi)011:388: sprul skur shar ba ngo mtshar che brjod med rnam
NK036(chi)011:389: par dag pa'i ye shes nyid stong par rang sar
NK036(chi)011:390: dag pa'i yul la snang ba ngo mtshar che ma
NK036(chi)011:391: rig mun sel thig le stong pa nyid dbang po'i
NK036(chi)011:392: yul la snang ba ngo mtshar che zhes brjod la
NK036(chi)011:393: de dag gi don yang bshad do de nas rdzogs
NK036(chi)011:394: pa chen po brjod pa las 'das pa'i don de
NK036(chi)011:395: skal ldan gyi blo la gnas par bya ba'i phyir
NK036(chi)011:396: 'di skad do dngos po gang la yang rang bzhin
NK036(chi)011:397: med pa yin no bltar med pa dang srog med
NK036(chi)011:398: pa dang snying po med pa dang ya ma barla
NK036(chi)011:399: yin pa dang tshig med pa dang yi ge med
NK036(chi)011:400: pa dang sgra med pa dang tha snyad med pa
NK036(chi)011:401: dang brjod du med pa'o zhes dngos po'i 'dug tshul
NK036(chi)011:402: brjod med du gtan la phebs pa'o de nas lus
NK036(chi)011:403: ngag yid gsum rdzogs pa chen po'i don stong nyid
NK036(chi)011:404: kyi go rar gzhug pa'i phyir stong pa nyid bde
NK036(chi)011:405: ba chen po'i ngang du dar cig bsgom de nyid
NK036(chi)011:406: kyi don brdas bskul ba'i phyir tshig tu 'di skad
NK036(chi)011:407: brjod par bya'o chos rnams thams cad stong zhin bdag
NK036(chi)011:408: med la 'dod cing zhen pa'i blo ni yong re
NK036(chi)011:409: 'khrul chos kyi dbyings nyid spros dang bral ba la
NK036(chi)011:410: mtshan ma tshig phyir 'brangs pa yong re 'gal snying
NK036(chi)011:411: po don gyi ye shes rang shar la gzhan byung
NK036(chi)011:412: rtsol grub byed pa yong re 'khrul sems gnyis skye
NK036(chi)011:413: shi gnyis las 'das pa la skye 'gag gnyis su
NK036(chi)011:414: 'dzin pa yongs re 'khrul 'bras bu rang rdzoogs smon
NK036(chi)011:415: lam bral ba la rnam dpyod dus la ltos pa
NK036(chi)011:416: yong re 'khrul bde sdug thams cad rig pa'i cho
NK036(chi)011:417: 'phrul la blang dor gnyis su 'dzin pa yong re
NK036(chi)011:418: 'khrul kun tu bzang po rang la gnas pa la
NK036(chi)011:419: yi dam gzhan nas 'tshol ba yong re 'khrul bdag
NK036(chi)011:420: nyid ye sangs rgyas pa yin pa la ngan song
NK036(chi)011:421: gsum du 'jog pa yong re 'khrul 'khor ba ngan
NK036(chi)011:422: song rol par ye shar la yang dag sangs rgyas
NK036(chi)011:423: 'dod pa yong re 'khrul dug lnga ma spangs rang
NK036(chi)011:424: byung chen po la nyon mongs spang byar 'dzin pa
NK036(chi)011:425: yong re 'khrul 'khrul pa'i snang ba chos sku rang
NK036(chi)011:426: snang la dngos po bdag tu 'dzin pa yong re
NK036(chi)011:427: 'khrul theg pa rim dgu rang la shar ba la
NK036(chi)011:428: so so'i 'dod gzhung 'dzin pa yong re 'khrul zhes
NK036(chi)011:429: tshig gis spro ba bskyed cing don bstan pa ra
NK036(chi)011:430: bya'o de'i rjes la lung bstan pa'i dbang ni spros
NK036(chi)011:431: pa med pa'i dbang la zhugs pas ngag gi sgrib
NK036(chi)011:432: pa yongs su dag nas ma 'ongs pa'i dus na
NK036(chi)011:433: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i zhing khams su skye bar 'gyur
NK036(chi)011:434: ro zhes brjod do rjes gnang ni spros med kyi
NK036(chi)011:435: dbang bskur nas sngags bzlas pa dang rdzogs rim rtsa
NK036(chi)011:436: dang rlung dang thig le rnams bsgom du rung ba
NK036(chi)011:437: dang thig le stong pa'i sgron ma nyid bsgom du
NK036(chi)011:438: rung ba'i rjes gnang thob bo dbugs dbyung ba ni
NK036(chi)011:439: khams gsum 'khor bar mi 'jug par byed pa'o gzengs
NK036(chi)011:440: bstod pa ni de ltar gyur pas sems la spob
NK036(chi)011:441: pa bskyed pa'o 'jug cing dbang bskur ba'i rim pa'o
NK036(chi)011:442: lasakyi mtha' bsdu ba ni rol ma'i sgra dang bcas
NK036(chi)011:443: pas gtor ma dbul zhing chos skyong rnams la sngar
NK036(chi)011:444: byas kyi gtang rag phyi ma'i khas len du byas
NK036(chi)011:445: la rbad bskul bya dkon mchog gi gtor ma dang
NK036(chi)011:446: yi dam gyi gtor ma dang mkha' 'gro dang chos
NK036(chi)011:447: skyong gi gtor ma dang 'byung po'i gtor ma rnams
NK036(chi)011:448: rim pa bzhin du dbul de nas rol mo'i sgra
NK036(chi)011:449: gong ma rnams dang ldan pas gtor ma rnams gshegs
NK036(chi)011:450: su gsol de nas bdag gi bskyed rim sngar bzhin
NK036(chi)011:451: du bsgom pas de'i dal bsdu ba dang rdo rje'i
NK036(chi)011:452: glu blangs pa dang bkra shis brjod pa dang smon
NK036(chi)011:453: lam btab ste rdo rje slob dpon dang rnal 'byor
NK036(chi)011:454: dbang phyug pho mo rnams kyis 'di ltar bya ste
NK036(chi)011:455: 'das dang ma 'ongs da ltar gyi rdzogs sangs rgyas
NK036(chi)011:456: pa'i legs pa yis bcom ldan rdo rje 'chang chen
NK036(chi)011:457: dang skal ba mnyam par 'gyur bar shog ngan song
NK036(chi)011:458: thams cad rgyun chad dang sangs rgyas bstan pa 'phel
NK036(chi)011:459: ba dang rdzogs sangs rgyas pa'i yon tan rnams bdag
NK036(chi)011:460: la deng 'dir stsal ba dang zhing khams bzang zhing
NK036(chi)011:461: nyams dga' bar bdag kyang skye 'gyur skye bar shog
NK036(chi)011:462: skyes pas sems can don byas te 'khor ba dong
NK036(chi)011:463: nas sprug par shog dong sprugs sangs rgyas chen po
NK036(chi)011:464: nyid rgyas par bdag la sems sbyong zhing bde bar
NK036(chi)011:465: mgon po rnams mnyam shog ji ltar dam tshig sdom
NK036(chi)011:466: pa nyid 'di nyid du yang rdzogs par shog ces
NK036(chi)011:467: smon lam dril bu'i sgra dang bcas par gdab cho
NK036(chi)011:468: ga lhag chad bskang ba'i yi ge brgya pa bzlas
NK036(chi)011:469: bum chus khrus byed na bya mi byed na ri'am
NK036(chi)011:470: gtsang sar bskyal man+dala phyags la dri bzang po'i chus
NK036(chi)011:471: byugs la me tog gcig tsam bzhag nang mchod byas
NK036(chi)011:472: pa'i snod dang rdzas thams cad bkrus la so so'i
NK036(chi)011:473: gnas su bzhag dbang bskur ba'i khang pa de lha
NK036(chi)011:474: khang ngam mchod khang yin na mchod pa bshams la
NK036(chi)011:475: bzhag gsar du brgyan pa yin na rgyan rnams bsdu
NK036(chi)011:476: rten rnams bsdus la gnas khang phyag la me tog
NK036(chi)011:477: gtor la bzhag snod ma yin pa la gsang ba'i
NK036(chi)011:478: don du dbang bskur bas rjes mi mngon par bya'o
NK036(chi)011:479: de nas yon dbul zhing dga' ston bya ba'i rim
NK036(chi)011:480: pa ni slob dpon la ci 'byor pa'i yon dbul
NK036(chi)011:481: mched grogs rnal 'byor pho mo rnams la dga' ston
NK036(chi)011:482: ci rigs par bya gzhan dge 'dun pa dang mgron
NK036(chi)011:483: po rnams la 'byor pa dang sbyar la spyan drangs
NK036(chi)011:484: de ltar byas pa'i yon tan ni rgyas par 'khor
NK036(chi)011:485: lo drug pa dang 'phra tig nas bstan par bya'o
NK036(chi)011:486: bkra shis pa'i yan lag yin pas slob dpon gyis
NK036(chi)011:487: dbu bzung nas mched lcam rnal 'byor pho mo la
NK036(chi)011:488: sogs rnams kyis glu gar la sogs par bya dge
NK036(chi)011:489: 'dun bzhugs na bkra shis byed du gzhug gzhan khye'u
NK036(chi)011:490: bu mo la sogs pas kyang glu gar dang rol
NK036(chi)011:491: mo la sogs pa shes tshad byed du gzhug 'thab
NK036(chi)011:492: pa dang rtsod pa dang khe grags kyi gtam rnams
NK036(chi)011:493: spang bar bya chos gtam yang tshogs kyi 'khor lor
NK036(chi)011:494: rtsod par 'gro bas mi bya gzhan ci dga' bya'o
NK036(chi)011:495: rin po che dbang gi phyag len ji lta ba
NK036(chi)011:496: bzhin bkod pa rdzogs so bla ma rdo rje 'chang
NK036(chi)011:497: ba'i lha lha yi lha khyod phyag 'tshal bstod bdag
NK036(chi)011:498: ni bskal pa thog med nas 'byung bzhi'i lus kyis
NK036(chi)011:499: bcings pa bdag 'byung bzhi'i gnad dang bral gyur nas
NK036(chi)011:500: dri med 'od gals lus ldan shog smra mang gang
NK036(chi)011:501: gis bcings pa bdag 'khrul pa'i gtam rgyud gzung zad
NK036(chi)011:502: nas brjod du med pa'i don ldan shog 'gyu byed
NK036(chi)011:503: rtogs pas bcings pa bdag mi rtog gsal ba'i snang
NK036(chi)011:504: mthong nas bsam pa'i 'phro 'du chad par shog de
NK036(chi)011:505: ltar lus ngag yid gsum la sku gsung thugs kyis
NK036(chi)011:506: byin brlabs pa'i 'bras bu sku gsum tshad phebs shog
